name: ShopsyLookerStudio

infos.name: Looker Studio Connector
infos.description:
Verbinden Sie ihren Shopware 6 Shop oder Shopware 6 Cloud Shop mit dem Looker Studio von Google (ehemals Google Data Studio), um ganz einfach interaktive Reports zu erstellen.


Es können Daten aus 17 verschiedenen Dimensionen gewählt werden:
  • Billing Address City
  • Shipping Address City
  • Billing Address Country
  • Shipping Address Country
  • Customer Group
  • Customer Number
  • Language
  • Order Total Amount Net
  • Order Number
  • Order State
  • Order Time
  • Order Total Amount
  • Payment Method
  • Payment State
  • Saleschannel
  • Shipping Costs
  • Total Orders
infos.installationManual:
Einfach über den Pluginmanager installieren und den Shop anschließend mit dem Looker Studio verbinden.
Unter "Erweiterungen->Looker Studio Connection-> Looker Studio Connection - Konfiguration" kann der Shop mit Looker Studio verbunden werden.

Kurzanleitung

infos.name: Looker Studio Connector
infos.description:
Connect your Shopware 6 Shop or Shopware 6 Cloud Shop to Google's Looker Studio (formerly Google Data Studio) to easily create interactive reports.

You can choose Data from 17 different dimensions:
  • Billing Address City
  • Shipping Address City
  • Billing Address Country
  • Shipping Address Country
  • Customer Group
  • Customer Number
  • Language
  • Order Total Amount Net
  • Order Number
  • Order State
  • Order Time
  • Order Total Amount
  • Payment Method
  • Payment State
  • Saleschannel
  • Shipping Costs
  • Total Orders
infos.installationManual:
Simply install it via the plugin manager and then connect the shop to Looker Studio.

The shop can be connected to Looker Studio under "Extensions->Looker Studio Connection-> Looker Studio Connection - Configuration".

Quick Guide
